136 with the orders of the patient's physician, an advanced practice registered nurse, or a
137 physician assistant; provided, however, that an agency shall be exempt from an additional
138 on-site licensure inspection if certified in a federal program for reimbursement of medicare
139 Medicare or Medicaid services."
